				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$^8$$\end{document} samples per detector per proton pulse, the computational efficiency was the mandatory requirement to be met in order for the data to be analysed within a reasonable time. Already the O(N2)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
