				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\tau $$\end{document} in order to estimate the counting losses that occurred in this specific region. As can be seen in Fig. 37, the experimental waiting time distribution recorded during the 240\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
