				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$^{\circ }$$\end{document} relative to the neutron beam direction, as described in Sect. 4.2 and in Ref. [128].

